00:01:09.950 --> 00:01:11.710
You just want a new lover, don't you?

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:12.660
Say it straight.

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:14.950
Don't beat around the bush.

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:18.230
Useless thing.

00:01:23.950 --> 00:01:24.950
Is it enough?

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:26.350
Can you let me go now?

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:36.600
You're here to investigate
Ye Changyuan too?

00:01:37.350 --> 00:01:38.710
You deliberately lured me here.

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:41.870
You are truly clever.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:43.950
Since our goals align,

00:01:44.950 --> 00:01:45.920
why not work together?

00:01:46.300 --> 00:01:46.920
What do you say?

00:01:47.900 --> 00:01:49.710
What leverage do you have
to bargain with me?

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.760
I know your secret.

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:54.920
Fine.

00:01:56.040 --> 00:01:58.400
We can't deal with Ye Changyuan yet.

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:00.000
I want to use him as bait

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:01.070
to catch a bigger fish.

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:03.510
We work together
to track Ye Changyuan's trail.

00:02:04.070 --> 00:02:04.870
Then,

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:06.920
we each take what we need.

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.250
Pleasure working with you.

00:02:21.150 --> 00:02:23.680
Wanyan Jin is indeed planning
to act against Su Guang.

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:25.630
Wait until he kills Su Guang,

00:02:26.470 --> 00:02:27.590
then I'll find another chance

00:02:27.750 --> 00:02:28.680
to get the account book.

00:02:32.430 --> 00:02:33.030
My Lord,

00:02:33.870 --> 00:02:36.000
