with the crown princess?

00:02:36.630 --> 00:02:37.840
I need to secure her first.

00:02:38.310 --> 00:02:39.630
Don't let her recklessness

00:02:39.960 --> 00:02:41.190
ruin my plan.

00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:43.710
I think

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:46.280
you're not just trying to secure her.

00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:48.910
Then why?

00:02:50.590 --> 00:02:54.000
He has feelings for the crown princess
and worries for her safety.

00:02:57.430 --> 00:02:58.120
Bai Ling,

00:02:58.750 --> 00:03:00.190
hit him ten times with a stick.

00:03:01.590 --> 00:03:02.150
Yes, My Lord.

00:03:03.190 --> 00:03:05.240
My Lord, I dare not
speak carelessly anymore.

00:03:16.520 --> 00:03:18.150
Wanyan Jin

00:03:19.500 --> 00:03:21.740
has been going out early
and coming back late these days.

00:03:21.740 --> 00:03:23.520
There's definitely something going on.

00:03:30.800 --> 00:03:31.800
Qingran.

00:03:41.750 --> 00:03:43.150
Where have you been these few days?

00:03:43.710 --> 00:03:44.750
