00:03:46.510 --> 00:03:48.260
I don't know what kind
of official business

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:49.750
must be handled at Begonia House.

00:03:50.630 --> 00:03:51.680
Begonia House?

00:03:51.900 --> 00:03:53.930
Have you been at Begonia House
these past few days?

00:03:54.150 --> 00:03:55.520
Qingran, perhaps you don't know it.

00:03:56.310 --> 00:03:57.690
Jin has recently become obsessed

00:03:57.700 --> 00:03:59.080
with the song and dance there.

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:01.260
